Hi Delphine.  Thanks for getting started on this.

We'd like the platform to just be `meta-yosemite4`.  Sentinel Dome is one of the compute cards that the chassis will support, but we shouldn't have to build separate images for different compute cards if we leverage entity-manager correctly.  The EM config should be yosemite4 for the chassis and sentinel-dome for the compute card.

According to yv2 named as meta-yosemitev2, would you like to consider that whether the new project name is meta-yosemite4 as saying above or meta-yosemitev4 which follows the same format with yv2? thank you.
Ack
